<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta http-equiv="content-type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
	<link rel="apple-touch-icon" sizes="180x180"    href="/favicons/apple-touch-icon.png">
	<link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="32x32" href="/favicons/favicon-32x32.png">
	<link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="16x16" href="/favicons/favicon-16x16.png">
	<link rel="manifest" href="/favicons/site.webmanifest">
  <link type="text/css" href="styles.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
  html {
        background: #F6FBFF;
  }
  main {
        max-width: 45em;
        margin-inline: auto;
  }


  h1 img {
        max-height: 2.25em;
	  margin-block: -0.33em 0;
          vertical-align: bottom;
          justify-self: center;
  }
  h1 img:first-of-type {
        transform: scaleX(-1);
  }

  h1 + p {
  	max-width: 100%;
        margin-block: 0.25em 1em;
        font-size: 1.25em;
        font-style: italic;
  }

  @media (max-width: 44em) {
  	h1 {
  		font-size: 3em;
  	}
  }
  @media (max-width: 33em) {

  	h1 {
  		font-size: 2em;
  	}
	  h1 + p {
	  	font-size: 1.1em;
	}
  }

  @media (max-width: 22em) {
  	h1 { display: block;
  		padding-block: 0.5em;
  	}
  	h1 img {
  		display: none;
  	}
	  h1 + p {
	  	font-size: 1em;
	}
  }

  .hero {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2,1fr);
      grid-gap: 1rem;
  }

  .hero #reports {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
  }

  .subtitle {
    font-size: 1.6rem;
    text-wrap: balance;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #022759;
  }

  .report-tile {
      background-color: #8FC0FF ;
      color: #022759;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-rows: repeat(3, max-content);
      border-radius: 16px;
      border: 2px solid #022759;
      padding: 1rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  h2.report-tile-title {
    padding: 0;
    border: 0px;
    margin-top: 0;
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  .report-tile img {
      max-width: 1.5rem;
      width: 100%;
  }

  #reports h2 [href] {
        display: block;
        color: inherit;
        text-underline-offset: 0.15em;
  }
  #reports h2 img[alt*="RSS"] {
 	display: block;
  	max-height: 2em;
  	margin: -0.2em;
  }

  #archive, #artchive details div {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
        grid-gap: 0 2em;
  }
 
  #archive details {
        padding-block: 0.5em;
        margin-block: 0 2em;
  }

  #archive details, #archive summary {
        grid-column: 1/-1;
  }

  #archive details ul {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0 1rem 1rem 1rem;
        list-style: none;
  }

  #archive details ul:nth-of-type(1) {
        grid-column: 1;
  }

  #archive details ul:nth-of-type(2) {
        grid-column: 2;
  }

  #archive details ul li {
        margin-inline: 0;
  }

  #archive details ul li [href] {
        display: block;
  }
  #reports details ul li [href]:hover,
  #archive details ul li [href]:hover {
        background: silver;
  }

  main footer  {
  	justify-content: center;
  	font-size: 1.1em;
  }
  main footer p {
  	margin-block: 0.5em;
  }
  main footer img {
  	vertical-align: -30%;
  }

.home-archive {
      border-radius: 16px;
}

details[open] > summary.home-archive {
      border-radius: 16px 16px 0px 0px;
}

.archive-list {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2,1fr);
      border: 2px solid #022759;
      background: #fff;
}

.archive-list h2 {
    background-color: #E3FFBF;
    font-size: 1rem;
    margin: 0;
    border: none;
    border-radius: 0;
    padding: 1rem;
}

.weekly {
      border-right: 2px solid #022759;
}


  @media (max-width: 33em) {

      .hero {
            grid-template-rows: repeat(2, min-content);
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      #archive, #archive details div {
            grid-template-rows: repeat(2, 1fr);
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            grid-gap: 1em;
      }

      .weekly {
            border-right: none;
      }
  }

  </style>
  <title>BCD Watch</title>
</head>
<body>
  <main>
    <div class="header">
    <h1 class="logo-style"><a href="https://bcd-watch.igalia.com"><img src="imgs/binoculars.svg" alt="" />BCD Watch</a></h1>
    </div>
    <div class="hero">
        <div class="hero-text">
            <p class="subtitle">Keeping an eye on changes to MDN’s Browser Compatibility Data</p>
            <p>This site automatically collects, indexes, and makes available for viewing (and as subscribe-able feeds), information about updates to <a href="https://github.com/mdn/browser-compat-data">Browser Compatibility Data (BCD)</a>. Currently there are two different views (and feeds) on this data, which are compiled each Tuesday (US/Eastern time).</p>
            <p>Perhaps you're interested in <a href="weekly/index.html">which changes were reported last week</a>, or more specifically <a href="weekly-completed/index.html">which features became "new baseline" last week</a> (marked as available in all 3 engines).</p>
        </div>
        <div id="reports">
            <div class="report-tile">
              <h2 class="report-tile-title"><a href="weekly">Full Weekly Report</a></h2> 
              <p>All the BCD updates that occurred in the last week: features added or removed, and which features gained or lost engine support.</p>
              <a href="weekly/feed.rss"><img src="imgs/rss-flat.svg" alt="RSS feed"></a>
              
            </div>
            <div class="report-tile">
              <h2 class="report-tile-title"><a href="weekly-completed">Baselines Weekly Report</a></h2>
              <p>All the BCD entries that moved to “<a href="https://web.dev/baseline">Baseline</a>: Newly available” status in the past week; i.e., are now supported in all three major browser engines.</p>
               <a href="weekly-completed/feed.rss"><img src="imgs/rss-flat.svg" alt="RSS feed"></a>
            </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div id="archive">
            <details>
            <summary class="home-archive">
            Archive of past reports, most to least recent
            </summary>
            <div class="archive-list">
              <div class="weekly">
                <h2>Full Weekly Report</h2>
                  <ul>
                  {{#each weekly}}
                  <li>
                  <a href="weekly/{{this}}">{{stripFileExtension this}}</a>
                  </li>{{/each}}
                  </ul>
              </div>
              <div class="baselines-weekly">
                <h2>Baselines Weekly Report</h2>
                <ul>
                  {{#each completed}}
                  <li>
                  <a href="weekly-completed/{{this}}">{{stripFileExtension this}}</a>
                  </li>{{/each}}
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
            </details>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <footer>
    <p>Brought to you by <a href="https://igalia.com"><img src="imgs/igalia-logo.png" alt="Igalia"></a></p>
    </footer>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
